Sabi pa niya

00:12:41.600 --> 00:12:42.800
na sa kabilang buhay,

00:12:43.080 --> 00:12:43.790
hindi pa rin niya kami makikilala

00:12:43.790 --> 00:12:45.150
bilang magkakapatid.

